column2: df <- resm %>%
mutate(Com = Comorbidities,
Year = Period,
Main = case_when(Diag == "Lung" ~ "Lung",
Diag == "Breast" ~"Breast",
Diag == "Colon" ~ "Colon",
T ~ "Remaining")) %>%
mutate(Main = fct_relevel(Main, "Remaining","Lung","Breast"))
Age           <- glm(cost ~ Age,           family = "poisson", data = df)
Year          <- glm(cost ~ Year,          family = "poisson", data = df)
Gender        <- glm(cost ~ Gender,        family = "poisson", data = df)
Diag          <- glm(cost ~ Diag,          family = "poisson", data = df)
Main          <- glm(cost ~ Main,          family = "poisson", data = df)
BMI           <- glm(cost ~ BMI,           family = "poisson", data = df)
Diagnoses     <- glm(cost ~ Diagnoses,     family = "poisson", data = df)
Comorbidities <- glm(cost ~ Comorbidities, family = "poisson", data = df)
Com           <- glm(cost ~ Com,           family = "poisson", data = df)
source("02_forestmodels_inter_age.R")
fit_uni_age <- list(Age, Year,Gender,Diag,BMI,Diagnoses,Comorbidities)
fit_mul_age <- glm(cost ~ Age * Year + Gender + BMI + Diagnoses + Comorbidities + Diag, family = "poisson", data = df)
i1 <- lars_forestmodel(fit = fit_mul_age, lst = fit_uni_age, palb = pala, pala="grey60",rmn=7)
source("02_forestmodels_inter_com.R")
fit_uni_com <- list(Com, Year,Gender,Diag,BMI,Diagnoses,Age)
fit_mul_com <- glm(cost ~ Com * Year + Gender + BMI + Diagnoses + Diag + Age, family = "poisson", data = df)
i2 <- lars_forestmodel(fit = fit_mul_com, lst = fit_uni_com, palb = pala, pala="grey60",rmn=5)
source("02_forestmodels_inter_dia.R")
fit_uni_dia <- list(Main, Year,Gender,BMI,Diagnoses,Comorbidities,Age)
fit_mul_dia <- glm(cost ~ Main * Year + Gender + BMI + Diagnoses + Comorbidities + Age, family = "poisson", data = df)
i3 <- lars_forestmodel(fit = fit_mul_dia, lst = fit_uni_dia, palb = pala, pala="grey60",rmn=7)
ap9 <- i1 + i2 + i3 + plot_layout(nrow=3, height=c(1,0.82,1)) + plot_annotation(tag_levels = "A")
